### 创建知识
POST http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "如何防范电信诈骗",
  "content": "电信诈骗的常见手法和防范措施...",
  "category": "防诈骗知识",
  "tags": "电信诈骗,防范措施",
  "authorId": 1
}

### 获取所有知识
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge

### 获取单个知识
GET http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/1

### 点赞知识
POST http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/1/like

### 删除知识
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/knowledge/1
